                    "name": "Amplify Voltage",
                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "text": "<b>Trigger</b> A shocker lizard within 20 feet makes a shock Strike or uses Discharge; <b>Effect</b> The shocker lizard lends some of its electrical power to the nearby lizard. This either causes the other lizard's shock Strike to lose the <a aonid=\"188\" game-obj=\"Traits\">nonlethal</a> trait or increases the DC of its Discharge to 20.",
